                                                                         成为超级节点或者投票可以获得DBC奖励
                                                             Being a super node or voting can earn you DBC rewards
                                                             
                                                             
1.成为超级节点有什么奖励？成为超级节点，从2021年5月到2024年5月，每天可以获得大于1.32万dbc的奖励. 所有超级节点1年奖励总数是1亿dbc

2.超级节点多长时间选举一次？每24小时选举一次，当选举的时候，节点质押dbc的数量和支持者投票的dbc数量总和排名前21名，就可以成为超级节点

3.投票也可以获得奖励吗？是的，投票的节点成为超级节点后，投票人也可以获得dbc奖励 ,查看地址：https://www.dbcwallet.io/#/staking

主网查看节点状态：https://telemetry.polkadot.io/#list/DBC%20Mainnet

主网钱包地址：https://www.dbcwallet.io/?rpc=wss%3A%2F%2Finfo.dbcwallet.io#/accounts

部署主网节点：https://github.com/DeepBrainChain/DeepBrainChain-MainChain/blob/master/docs/join_dbc_network.md

如何给节点投票：https://github.com/DeepBrainChain/DeepBrainChain-MainChain/blob/master/docs/How%20do%20I%20participate%20in%20SuperNode 

如何给节点投票详细介绍（来源社区）：https://bihu.com/article/1930794414




1.What are the rewards for being a super node?   Become a super node and you can earn more than 13,200 DBC per day

2.How often are supernodes elected?     
       Elections are held every 24 hours. At the time of election, a node with the number of pledged DBC and the number of votes of its supporters ranking 
  in the top 21 can become a super node

3. Can I also get rewards for voting?   Yes, voters can also receive DBC rewards when the voting node becomes a super node

View the nodes：https://telemetry.polkadot.io/#list/DBC%20Mainnet

MainNet wallet：https://www.dbcwallet.io/?rpc=wss%3A%2F%2Finfo.dbcwallet.io#/accounts

Deploy mainNet node：https://github.com/DeepBrainChain/DeepBrainChain-MainChain/blob/master/docs/join_dbc_network_EN.md

How do I vote for nodes：https://github.com/DeepBrainChain/DeepBrainChain-MainChain/blob/master/docs/staking_dbc_and_voting_EN.md
